&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Then, upload files in the &lt;em&gt;public&lt;/em&gt; folder to middleware folder(eg. html folder in nginx)&lt;/p&gt;
